            <h2>Gameplay</h2>
            

            <p>
                The Alchemist is a Life you can choose in the game Fantasy Life. It is one of 12 Lives that can be 
                chosen at any time during the game by visiting the Guild Master (except during a story mission).

                The Alchemist uses flasks to make medicine, bombs, flasks and accessories. There are 67 alchemist recipes in the 
                base game and 90 with the DLC.
            </p>

            <h2>Skills</h2>

            <p>
                When the player chooses the Alchemist life, they learn 3 skills: Alchemy, Compound Alchemy, and Accessory Alchemy. 
                The max skill level is 15 (20 with the DLC). To unlock the new cap, you must reach Legend rank and talk to Divinus 
                with the Alchemist Life activated. He will increase the cap of all 3 skills to 20 and upgrade the licence to 
                God-in-Training rank.
            </p>
